---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import Cat from "../assets/cat1.jpg"
---
<aside class="sticky top-20 scroll-pt-26 bg-background border-2 border-muted/40 px-6 py-10 rounded-md flex flex-col items-center font-inter h-fit text-text max-w-100">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
      <Image class="w-60 h-80 rounded-md object-cover" src={Cat} alt="A hard image of a cool cat with a trasher shirt"/>
      <h2 class="text-center font-bold text-3xl pt-10">Alejandro Camacho</h2>
    </div>
    <p class="text-md pt-20 text-center text-muted">Building APIs, wrangling databases, and making terminals look cool.</p>
  </aside>
